      <title>韩国央行决心控制价格并逐步走向中性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bok-keeps-rate-on-hold-opting-for-steady-stance-after-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行维持基准利率不变，同时调整指引，暗示不会“长期”维持限制性立场，尽管保持开放选择，但仍逐渐接近中性立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bok-keeps-rate-on-hold-opting-for-steady-stance-after-polls</guid>
